!!!  
%html.no-js
  %head
    %meta{:charset=>"utf-8"}
    %meta{"http-equiv"=> "X-UA-Compatible", :content=>"IE=edge,chrome=1"}
    %title Oahu, connect with your audience, anywhere.
    %meta{:name=>"author", :content=>"Oahu"}
    %meta{:viewport=>"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"}
    %link{:rel=>"shortcut icon", :href=>"/favicon.ico"}
    %link{:rel=>"apple-touch-icon", :href=>"/apple-touch-icon.png"}
    %meta{:name=>"viewport", :content=>"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"}
    %link{:rel => "stylesheet", :href=> "/assets/fonts/stylesheet.css" }
    %link{:rel => "stylesheet", :href=> "/assets/vendor/bootstrap.min.css" }
    %link{:rel => "stylesheet", :href=> "/assets/vendor/bootstrap-responsive.min.css" }
    %link{:rel => "stylesheet", :href=> "/assets/css/style.css" }
    %script{:src=>"http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"}
  %body
    %header.navbar.navbar-fixed-top
      .navbar-inner
        .container
          %a.brand{:href=>"/"} oahu
          %a.btn.btn-navbar{'data-toggle'=>'collapse', 'data-target'=>'.nav-collapse'}
            %span.icon-bar
            %span.icon-bar
            %span.icon-bar
          .nav-collapse
            %ul.nav
              %li
                %a{:href=>'#product'} Product
              %li
                %a{:href=>'clients'} Clients
              %li
                %a{:href=>'contact'} Contact
              %li
                %a{:href=>'jobs'} Jobs
              %li
                %a.contact{:href=>'mailto:contact@oahu.fr'} contact@oahu.fr

    .container
      .hero-unit
        %h1
          Connect with your audience,
          %em anywhere
        %h2
          Oahu creates long term, meaningful relationships
          %br
          between you and your community
          
      %section#product
        .page-header
          %h1 Product
        .row
          .span3
            %h2
              Oahu is an integrated
              %br
              marketing platform.
            that enables you to build richer, more engaging campaigns. Be assured that your campaign is optimized for engagement.

          .span3.offset1
            %h2 Simple to use
            Publish our pre-built apps to instantly offer your fans Quizzes, Instant Wins, branded pages and more. You can build entire campaigns without a single line of code

          .span3.offset1
            %h2 Full service
            We handle the media, games mechanics, and user generated contents that make your campaigns richer and more compelling.

        .row
          .span3
            %h2 Rich realtime api
            Use a robust set of rich realtime push components to create even more ambitious campaigns at a fraction of the time and cost.

          .span3.offset1
            %h2 Complete Metrics
            With integrated metrics, Oahu enables you to get a precise overview of how your campaign’s doing, who’s playing, who’s sharing and much, much more.

          .span3.offset1
            %h2 Cross campaign marketing
            Most importantly, We do all of this and more with an easy to use single sign-on, that enables your fans to enrich their profile campaign after campaign, allowing you to offer them precisely what makes them tick 

      %section
        .row
          .span4
            #clients.page-header
              %h1 Clients
            %ul.clients
              %li.universal Universal
              %li.pathe Pathé
              %li.orange Orange

          .span3
            #contact.page-header
              %h1 Contact
            %h2
              Oahu is currently
              %br
              a subscription service.
            We plan on opening it to public in the future, but for now you can get a demo by contacting us. We’ll be sure to get back to you !
            %br
            %br
            .contact
              %a.btn.btn-large{:href=>'mailto:contact@oahu.fr'} contact@oahu.fr
          .span3.offset1
            #jobs.page-header
              %h1 Jobs
            %h2 We’re  currently looking for : 
            %ul
              %li A Front-end developer who knows CSS3 and browsers perfectly
              %li A Chief of product with a keen eye for detail and insatiable need for perfection
            .jobs
              %a.btn.btn-large{:href=>'mailto:jobs@oahu.fr'} jobs@oahu.fr
      :javascript
        document.createElement('section');
        document.createElement('header');
      %script{:src=>"//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1/jquery.min.js"}
      %script{:src=>'/assets/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.js'}
      %script{:src=>'/assets/js/ga.js'}
      %script{:src=>'/assets/js/app.js'}
